---
import AppLayout from '../../layouts/AppLayout.astro';
---

<AppLayout
  title="Prototipos de Baja Fidelidad"
  subtitle="Wireframes interactivos de flujo y pantallas principales de MeetingVoice"
  currentPath="/design/lowfidelity"
>
  <div class="space-y-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header info -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-800/80 pb-4">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 font-mono">Práctica XP: Diseño Simple & Prototipado Rápido</p>
      </div>
      <span class="text-xs font-mono text-zinc-400 bg-zinc-900 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-zinc-800"
        >Fase: Iteración 1</span
      >
    </div>

    <!-- Wireframes Roster -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Pantalla 1: Landing Page -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/40 p-5 space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-850 pb-2.5">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-200 font-mono">[Pantalla 1] Landing Page de MeetingVoice</span>
          <span
            class="text-[9px] font-mono text-indigo-400 bg-indigo-500/5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-indigo-500/10"
            >Home</span
          >
        </div>

        <!-- Wireframe mock body -->
        <div class="border border-dashed border-zinc-700/60 rounded-xl p-4 bg-zinc-900/10 space-y-4 text-center">
          {/* Header placeholder */}
          <div
            class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-dashed border-zinc-800 pb-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-600"
          >
            <span>[Logo] MeetingVoice</span>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <span>[Características]</span>
              <span>[Precios]</span>
              <span>[Iniciar Sesión]</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Hero */}
          <div class="py-6 space-y-3.5">
            {/* SVG Microphone central */}
            <div
              class="mx-auto w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-dashed border-zinc-700 flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="16"
                height="16"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#71717a"
                stroke-width="2.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3Z"></path>
                <path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"></path>
                <line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="22"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-1.5 max-w-xs mx-auto">
              <div class="h-4 bg-zinc-800 rounded w-full border border-zinc-700/50"></div>
              <div class="h-2.5 bg-zinc-800/60 rounded w-3/4 mx-auto"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-2 flex justify-center gap-2">
              <div
                class="h-7 w-24 rounded bg-zinc-700 border border-zinc-600 text-[10px] font-mono flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-400 font-semibold"
              >
                [CTA: Registrar]
              </div>
              <div
                class="h-7 w-20 rounded bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 text-[10px] font-mono flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-500"
              >
                [Demo]
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Features cards grid */}
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 border-t border-dashed border-zinc-800 pt-3">
            <div class="border border-dashed border-zinc-800 rounded p-2 space-y-1 text-left">
              <div class="h-1.5 bg-zinc-800 rounded w-3/4"></div>
              <div class="h-1 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded w-full"></div>
              <div class="h-1 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded w-5/6"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-dashed border-zinc-800 rounded p-2 space-y-1 text-left">
              <div class="h-1.5 bg-zinc-800 rounded w-2/3"></div>
              <div class="h-1 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded w-full"></div>
              <div class="h-1 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded w-2/3"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-dashed border-zinc-800 rounded p-2 space-y-1 text-left">
              <div class="h-1.5 bg-zinc-800 rounded w-4/5"></div>
              <div class="h-1 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded w-full"></div>
              <div class="h-1 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded w-3/4"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pantalla 2: Grabación de Reunión -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/40 p-5 space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-850 pb-2.5">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-200 font-mono">[Pantalla 2] Grabación de Sesión</span>
          <span
            class="text-[9px] font-mono text-amber-400 bg-amber-500/5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-amber-500/10"
            >HU-01 + HU-02</span
          >
        </div>

        <!-- Wireframe mock body -->
        <div class="border border-dashed border-zinc-700/60 rounded-xl p-4 bg-zinc-900/10 space-y-4 text-center">
          <div
            class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-dashed border-zinc-800 pb-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-600"
          >
            <span>[Sesión Activa: 02:45]</span>
            <span class="text-rose-500 animate-pulse">● GRABANDO</span>
          </div>

          {/* Transcription Area Box */}
          <div
            class="border border-dashed border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-3 h-28 bg-zinc-950/50 text-left space-y-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-500 overflow-y-auto"
          >
            <p>
              <span class="text-zinc-400 font-bold">[Participante 1]:</span> Hola, hoy vamos a revisar el diseño de base de
              datos...
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class="text-zinc-400 font-bold">[Participante 2]:</span> De acuerdo, Kevin debería migrar a IndexedDB
              esta semana.
            </p>
            <div class="h-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded w-1/3 animate-pulse"></div>
          </div>

          {/* Audio Waves Simulation */}
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-1 py-1.5 h-6">
            <span class="h-2 w-1 rounded bg-zinc-700"></span>
            <span class="h-4 w-1 rounded bg-zinc-600"></span>
            <span class="h-5 w-1 rounded bg-zinc-500"></span>
            <span class="h-3 w-1 rounded bg-zinc-600"></span>
            <span class="h-5 w-1 rounded bg-zinc-500"></span>
            <span class="h-2 w-1 rounded bg-zinc-700"></span>
          </div>

          {/* Buttons controls */}
          <div class="flex gap-2 justify-center">
            <div
              class="h-7 w-28 rounded bg-rose-500/10 border border-rose-500/35 text-[9px] font-mono flex items-center justify-center text-rose-400 font-semibold"
            >
              [■ Finalizar Reunión]
            </div>
            <div
              class="h-7 w-20 rounded bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 text-[9px] font-mono flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-400"
            >
              [⏸ Pausar]
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pantalla 3: Resumen de Extracción -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/40 p-5 space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-850 pb-2.5">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-200 font-mono">[Pantalla 3] Resumen de Extracción</span>
          <span
            class="text-[9px] font-mono text-indigo-400 bg-indigo-500/5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-indigo-500/10"
            >HU-04</span
          >
        </div>

        <!-- Wireframe mock body -->
        <div class="border border-dashed border-zinc-700/60 rounded-xl p-4 bg-zinc-900/10 space-y-4 text-center">
          <div
            class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-dashed border-zinc-800 pb-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-600"
          >
            <span>[Extracción LLM Completada]</span>
            <span class="text-emerald-400">✓ PROCESADO</span>
          </div>

          {/* Task rows list */}
          <div class="space-y-2 text-left">
            <div
              class="border border-dashed border-zinc-800 rounded p-2.5 bg-zinc-950/30 flex items-center justify-between text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-400"
            >
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <span class="font-bold text-zinc-200">[Tarea 1] Migrar BD a IndexedDB</span>
                <div class="flex gap-2 text-zinc-500">
                  <span>Resp: [Kevin Palacios]</span>
                  <span>Plazo: [2026-05-30]</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-zinc-600 cursor-pointer">[Editar / Eliminar]</span>
            </div>

            <div
              class="border border-dashed border-zinc-800 rounded p-2.5 bg-zinc-950/30 flex items-center justify-between text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-400"
            >
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <span class="font-bold text-zinc-200">[Tarea 2] Definir proveedor LLM</span>
                <div class="flex gap-2 text-zinc-500">
                  <span>Resp: [Jahir Rocha]</span>
                  <span>Plazo: [2026-06-02]</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-zinc-600 cursor-pointer">[Editar / Eliminar]</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Bottom actions */}
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-t border-dashed border-zinc-800 pt-2.5">
            <div
              class="h-6 w-20 rounded bg-zinc-850 border border-zinc-700 text-[8px] font-mono flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-400"
            >
              [+ Añadir manual]
            </div>
            <div
              class="h-7 w-28 rounded bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/35 text-[9px] font-mono flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 font-semibold"
            >
              [✓ Confirmar y Guardar]
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pantalla 4: Dashboard de Pendientes -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/40 p-5 space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-850 pb-2.5">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-200 font-mono">[Pantalla 4] Dashboard de Pendientes</span>
          <span
            class="text-[9px] font-mono text-emerald-400 bg-emerald-500/5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-emerald-500/10"
            >HU-05 + HU-06</span
          >
        </div>

        <!-- Wireframe mock body -->
        <div class="border border-dashed border-zinc-700/60 rounded-xl p-4 bg-zinc-900/10 space-y-4 text-center">
          <div
            class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-dashed border-zinc-800 pb-2 text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-600"
          >
            <span>[Tareas Guardadas]</span>
            <span>Orden: [Fecha Límite Ascendente]</span>
          </div>

          {/* Tasks list with checkboxes */}
          <div class="space-y-1.5 text-left text-[9px] font-mono text-zinc-400">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 rounded bg-zinc-950/40 border border-dashed border-zinc-850">
              <span
                class="w-3.5 h-3.5 border border-dashed border-zinc-700 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] text-transparent"
                >✓</span
              >
              <div class="flex-1 flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-zinc-300 font-medium">Migrar base de datos a IndexedDB</span>
                <span class="text-zinc-500 font-bold">2026-05-30</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 rounded bg-zinc-950/40 border border-dashed border-zinc-850">
              <span
                class="w-3.5 h-3.5 border border-dashed border-zinc-700 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] text-transparent"
                >✓</span
              >
              <div class="flex-1 flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-zinc-300 font-medium">Definir proveedor de LLM con cliente</span>
                <span class="text-zinc-500 font-bold">2026-06-02</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 rounded bg-zinc-950/40 border border-dashed border-zinc-850 opacity-60"
            >
              <span
                class="w-3.5 h-3.5 border border-dashed border-emerald-500/40 rounded bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] text-emerald-400 font-bold"
                >✓</span
              >
              <div class="flex-1 flex justify-between line-through">
                <span class="text-zinc-500">Diseñar wireframe de baja fidelidad</span>
                <span class="text-zinc-600 font-bold">2026-05-27</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Stats quick overview */}
          <div
            class="border-t border-dashed border-zinc-800 pt-2 flex justify-between items-center text-[8px] font-mono text-zinc-500"
          >
            <span>Completadas: 1/3</span>
            <span>Pendientes: 2</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Flows connector text description -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/20 p-5 space-y-3 font-sans text-xs text-zinc-400">
      <h4 class="font-bold text-zinc-200">Flujo General del Software</h4>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">
        El flujo se diseña de manera lineal e intuitiva:
        <br />
        1. El usuario arriba a la **Landing Page (Home)** donde lee las bondades de automatización del acta.
        <br />
        2. Presiona "Iniciar" y accede a la **Grabación de Sesión (Consola)**. Acepta permisos de voz e inicia la transcripción
        en vivo.
        <br />
        3. Al presionar "Finalizar", el sistema procesa el texto en segundo plano y muestra el **Resumen de Extracción LLM**
        donde el usuario edita o depura los acuerdos.
        <br />
        4. Al confirmar, las tareas son guardadas en base de datos local y renderizadas en tiempo real en el **Dashboard de
        Pendientes** organizadas cronológicamente para evitar pérdidas de plazos.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Client approval footnote footer -->
    <footer class="text-center py-6 border-t border-zinc-800/80 font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500">
      Low Fidelity — Iteración 1. Aprobado por: <span class="text-zinc-300 font-semibold">Ariel Rosas (Cliente)</span>.
    </footer>
  </div>
</AppLayout>
